import nltk
nltk.download('punkt')
from nltk import word_tokenize
from nltk import ngrams

tokenized_docs = []
for doc in docs:
    tokens = word_tokenize(doc)
    print('1: ',tokens)

    # 取n-gram
    bigram = ngrams(tokens,n=2) #n =2代表Bi gram
    trigram = ngrams(tokens,n=3) #n =3代表Tri gram
    #為object ，可迭代 用for loop


    # 以底線合併tri-gram
    bigram = ['_'.join(x) for x in bigram]    #x 是tuple，即為分割好的詞   #'_'.join(x) 兩兩以底線相接
    trigram = ['_'.join(x) for x in trigram]     #'_'.join(x) 每三個以底線相接
    print('2: ',bigram)
    print('3: ',trigram)
    print()

    # 將三種n元語法的詞彙合併
    tokens = tokens + bigram + trigram

    # 以空白合併為文件
    doc = ' '.join(tokens)
    tokenized_docs.append(doc)

# 計算tf-idf
from sklearn.feature_extraction.text import TfidfVectorizer

vectorizer = TfidfVectorizer()
tfidf_matrix = vectorizer.fit_transform(tokenized_docs)
tfidfs = tfidf_matrix.toarray()
tokens = vectorizer.get_feature_names()
pd.DataFrame(tfidfs,columns=tokens)
